veryone happy with loot decision, but at least they will know they have a fair chance of geting something too.<br>
<br>
As for random - if it works for you then enough said. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Casai the Troll       ~#~</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
